     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">a</span>
     </div>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">v</span>
      <div class="msup">
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mi">v</span>
       </div>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mi">′</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mrow">
     <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mi">t</span>
     </div>
     <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>, where 
  <span class="italic">v</span> and 
  <span class="italic">v</span>′ are the initial vibrational quantum numbers of the diatoms. The vibrational wavefunction is initialized as the product of the Morse functions 
